data.description: $25,000 REDUCTION!!!! MOTIVATED SELLER!!!! Check out this 4bed/2bath on 4+ acres off Swan Lake RD. This home is 4-sided brick ranch with a screened in front and back porch. 2 car carport and huge workshop w/ electricity out back. Roof (2011) HVAC (2007) double pane window throughout (2012). There are 2 wells on the property and public water supply. This property is 4 parcels of land combine into 1, includes wooded and open land. Lots of potential here, call today!!
